  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Community Stabilization Activity (CSA)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project provides the Government of Colombia (GOC) with technical assistance and tools to address the emerging humanitarian crisis createdin communities affected by the sudden increase of population flows from Venezuela. The intervention will comprehensively respond to needs, promoting overall community stability, and social and cultural integration. The project includes the set up of a registry of migrants, awareness raising in communities to foster integration and the provisionof health services to the most vulnerable populations.</narrative>
  </description>
